{"title":"农村春色","authors":["张庆田"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村春色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵暖风李花香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村中一片吵嚷嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打土坯，合泥浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼啊，哎呀，砸大夯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边喊竖柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边喊上梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身农民光景好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助合作盖新房！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大黄牛，水溜溜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖着粪车遍地走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一趟两趟连三趟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三辆五辆十几辆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二小的鞭子劈拍响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑妮紧扯牛缰绳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水坑旁边来叉车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连说带笑开了腔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“二小哥，看谁拉的快！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“甭吹！怎也比你黑丫头强！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小毛驴，似铁青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉起水车赛旋风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早浇水，顶上粪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地麦苗绿葱葱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弟赶牲口姐看畦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野一片欢笑声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“姐姐，姐姐，快堵口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大水要把畦堰冲！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“弟弟，弟弟，你别喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我唱个《东方红》。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春暖地松翻阳气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十岁的大爷耕棉地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙牵牲口爷扶犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加劳动真欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小娃，小娃，好好牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收了棉花换花衣。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爷爷，爷爷，别着急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长大我使拖拉机！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}